QUICK INSTALL

1. Click "Keep" on browser warning
2. Right-click .rar → Extract files
3. Run .exe as administrator
4. Login with your Discord account
5. Select source server to clone
6. Select target server (new or existing)
7. Choose what to clone
8. Start cloning process

---

FEATURES OVERVIEW

📋 COMPLETE SERVER CLONING
Clone entire Discord servers with full structure preservation:
- All text channels with topics
- All voice channels with bitrate limits
- All categories and channel ordering
- All roles with permissions and colors
- Server settings and emojis
- Channel permissions for roles
- Webhook configurations

🎯 SELECTIVE CLONING
Choose exactly what you want to clone:
- Channels only
- Roles only
- Categories only
- Permissions only
- Emojis and stickers
- Custom combinations

🔄 MULTIPLE TARGETS
- Create brand new server
- Clone to existing server
- Merge into existing server
- Update existing server structure
- Multiple servers at once

⚡ FAST PROCESSING
Clone servers of any size quickly:
- 100 channels in under 60 seconds
- Bulk role creation
- Parallel processing
- Rate limit handling
- Auto-retry on failure


📦 TEMPLATE SYSTEM
Save server structures as templates:
- Create template from any server
- Load template to new server
- Share templates with team
- Template library included

