---

WHAT CAN BE CLONED

✅ TEXT CHANNELS
Channel names, topics, slowmode, NSFW status, category placement, permission overwrites

✅ VOICE CHANNELS
Channel names, bitrate, user limit, category placement, permission overwrites

✅ CATEGORIES
Category names, channel ordering inside, permission overwrites

✅ ROLES
Role names, colors, permissions, hoist status, mentionability, position order

✅ PERMISSIONS
Role permissions, channel-specific overwrites, category-level permissions

✅ EMOJIS & STICKERS
Custom emoji names and images (rate limited)

✅ SERVER SETTINGS
Server name, icon, region, verification level, explicit content filter

